<title>USA: Veritas sets 3-for-2 stock split.</title>
<headline>Veritas sets 3-for-2 stock split.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. 1997-07-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Veritas Software Corp said Wednesday its board of directors has approved a three-for-two stock split.</p>
<p>Shareholders of record on August 28, will receive one additional share for every two shares of common stock held, payable on September 12.</p>
<p>Veritas has about 20.3 million shares outstanding. The split will increase shares outstanding to about 30.4 million.</p>
